metadata.name: Toddlers and Tiaras
metadata.summary: Toddlers & Tiaras follows families on their quest for crowns, big titles and lots of cash.
metadata.description: On any given weekend across the country, toddlers take the stage wearing makeup, spray tans and fake hair to be judged on beauty, personality and costumes. Toddlers & Tiaras follows families on their quest for sparkly crowns, big titles and lots of cash.
